Run the LPA_host_agent.sh script from a cron job.

Pull statistics for:
Network
CPU (overall and per process)
Memory (overall and per process)
Disk (overall and per process

Tools:

*Network*
- ethtool with the statistics flag
ethtool -S <device name>

*Memory*
top -b -n1 -o %MEM
vmstat, free

*CPU*
- Batch mode top:
top (top -b -n1)

*Disk*
- iostat (iostat - Report Central Processing Unit (CPU) statistics and input/output statistics for devices, partitions and network filesystems (NFS).)


These statistics are dumped to temporary files which will be scpi'd ovr to the aggregator server (pulled by the aggregator server)
